    <item>
      <title>亚马逊因人工智能担忧而下沉，贝索斯财富缩水 210 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/bezos-wealth-drops-by-21-billion-as-amazon-sinks-on-ai-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司表示计划继续在人工智能领域投入巨资，即使以牺牲短期利润为代价，杰夫·贝佐斯的财富因此缩水逾 210 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/bezos-wealth-drops-by-21-billion-as-amazon-sinks-on-ai-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克向阻止创纪录薪酬协议的法官做出最后陈述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/musk-makes-final-pitch-to-judge-who-blocked-record-pay-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克为挽救特斯拉公司 560 亿美元的薪酬方案而进行的长达六年的法律斗争于周五拉开帷幕，这位世界首富向法官做出了最后的辩护，法官裁定薪酬协议存在缺陷并将其驳回。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/musk-makes-final-pitch-to-judge-who-blocked-record-pay-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 15:26:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克 100 指数进入调整区间，人工智能宠儿股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nasdaq-100-is-in-correction-territory-with-ai-darlings-sinking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大型科技公司的剧烈轮动导致纳斯达克 100 指数陷入回调区域，短短三周内市值蒸发逾 2 万亿美元，交易员平仓了一年多来获利颇丰的头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nasdaq-100-is-in-correction-territory-with-ai-darlings-sinking</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:47:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卖空者左翼删除的推文在欺诈案中再次出现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/short-seller-andrew-left-s-deleted-tweets-reappear-in-fraud-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的卖空者安德鲁·莱夫特 (Andrew Left) 去年删除了其研究公司的全部推文历史，以抵御当时他所说的“集体诉讼律师和巨魔”，他们想在他过去的股票评论中寻找污点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/short-seller-andrew-left-s-deleted-tweets-reappear-in-fraud-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疲软前景掩盖盈利增长，Booking 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/booking-beats-on-room-nights-even-as-travel-spending-slows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Booking Holdings Inc. 是 Kayak 和 Priceline 等近十几个旅游品牌的母公司，尽管其第二季度业绩大多超出分析师预期，但第三季度的业绩预测却令人失望。该公司股价在周五交易中下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/booking-beats-on-room-nights-even-as-travel-spending-slows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:09:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MercadoLibre 第二季度表现强劲，抵御科技股抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mercadolibre-meli-tops-estimates-with-profit-doubling-from-year-ago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲大型电子商务和支付公司 MercadoLibre Inc. 的第二季度收益超出分析师预期，其股价飙升，抵消了科技公司和地区同行的下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/mercadolibre-meli-tops-estimates-with-profit-doubling-from-year-ago</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:08:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DoorDash 盈利前景强劲，送货订单增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/doordash-posts-strong-profit-outlook-growth-in-delivery-orders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DoorDash Inc. 股价创下九个月来最大单日涨幅，此前该公司公布了本季度好于预期的利润预测，表明客户需求具有弹性，并且进军餐厅以外新领域的计划已取得成效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/doordash-posts-strong-profit-outlook-growth-in-delivery-orders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:06:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
